Name: Crazy Fatties
About the game: Crazy Fatties is a casual level-breaking game. You can experience all game levels after purchase. Through the operation, the player avoids danger, defeats the enemy, reaches the end within the stipulated time, and finally gets rewards! There are different types of levels, such as encountering flames, encountering floods, or more enemies! Each has a unique experience. Players can also enjoy the fun of collecting, gaining gold coins by winning the game in exchange for different character appearances.
